OL,4,Cwas semi conscious in her own home
OL,6,FA son subjected his 76-year-old mother
OL,7,Fto an attack which fractured her spine
OL,8,Fand left her face "black and blue."
OL,10,FDylan Thompson kicked, stamped and
OL,11,Fpunched his mum in her own home in
OL,12,FSouth Shields, seriously injuring her.
OL,14,FHe then dragged her bleeding body
OL,15,Facross the floor before leaving her in
OL,16,Fa semi-conscious state before she was
OL,17,Ffound by her granddaughter.
