OL,3,CSon beat his 76-year-old mum until she
OL,4,Cwas semi conscious in her own home
OL,6,FNewcastle Crown Court heard the
OL,7,Fpensioner had extensive bruising to
OL,8,Fher face and head, a fractured
OL,9,Fvertebrae and a deep cut to her leg
OL,10,Fwhich went down to the bone.
OL,12,FThompson, 36, who has 72 previous
OL,13,Fconvictions, was initially charged
OL,14,Fwith grievous bodily harm (GBH) with
OL,15,Fintent but prosecutors accepted his
OL,16,Fguilty plea to the lesser offence of
OL,17,FGBH.
OL,19,FHe has now been jailed for two years
OL,20,Fand six months.
