OL,3,CSon beat his 76-year-old mum until she
OL,4,Cwas semi conscious in her own home
OL,6,FThe attack happened in the victim's
OL,7,Fhome in South Shields on May 21 last
OL,8,Fyear. When her granddaughter found her
OL,9,Fshe was semi-conscious and unable to
OL,10,Fget up.
OL,12,FThe victim told her granddaughter she
OL,13,Fhad been punched, kicked and stamped
OL,14,Fon by her son.
OL,16,FThe court heard there was blood all
OL,17,Fover and it looked like she had been
OL,18,Fdragged through a passageway due to
OL,19,Fsmeared blood marks.
