OL,6,FA cupboard had been cleared, exposing
OL,7,Fthe entrance to the cellar.
OL,9,FThe victim later said Thompson, of no
OL,10,Ffixed address, had been kickboxing in
OL,11,Ffront of her face and then started to
OL,12,Fassault her.
OL,14,FShe appeared reluctant to get him in
OL,15,Ftrouble but was fearful of him.
OL,17,FShe was described by her granddaughter
OL,18,Fas being black and blue on her face
OL,19,Fand head and was in hospital for 19
OL,20,Fdays.
