OL,6,FRecorder Felicity Davies said images
OL,7,Fof the bruising to her head, face and
OL,8,Fneck were "shocking" and added: "The
OL,9,Fphotographs of the defendant's mother
OL,10,Fare appalling.
OL,12,F"There are very extensive bruising
OL,13,Finjuries to her face, head and neck.
OL,14,FThe granddaughter was not exaggerating
OL,15,Fwhen she said her grandmother was
OL,16,Fblack and blue."
OL,18,FVic Laffey, defending, said he was
OL,19,Fdrunk and is of "limited intellect".
